short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Share your dankest images in one click

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Manage webhooks and instantly share dank images you come across !

When Dank Share is active, it will try to add a small button to every image you can find on a tab.
Clicking this button will instantly share the attached image to every webhook you have set as an embed message.
Yep, that's it, simple isn't it ?
